
# 🚗 Tesla Deliveries & Production Analysis (2015–2025)

> **An End-to-End Machine Learning Pipeline for Predicting Tesla Vehicle Deliveries using Regression Models and Time Series Forecasting**

---

## 📖 Project Overview

This project implements a complete **Machine Learning pipeline** using Tesla's deliveries and production dataset spanning **2015–2025**. The workflow covers data exploration, feature engineering, predictive modeling, model optimization, statistical validation, and time-series forecasting to analyze delivery trends and estimate future demand.

The project demonstrates the complete lifecycle of a supervised machine learning workflow, from raw data analysis to forecasting and model evaluation.

---

## 📊 Dataset Information

| Attribute           | Details                               |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| **Dataset**         | Tesla Deliveries & Production Dataset |
| **Time Period**     | 2015 – 2025                           |
| **Records**         | 2640                                  |
| **Features**        | 12                                    |
| **Target Variable** | `Estimated_Deliveries`                |
| **Problem Type**    | Regression + Time Series Forecasting  |

